title: Jokes, Glamour and a Try for Normalcy as Correspondents Dinner Returns

sentence: What if I make a really mean joke about Kellyanne Conway and her husband rushes up on the stage and thanks me?? What I like about Ron DeSantis is if Trump was the original Terminator, DeSantis is like the T-1000.
